#Release notes 26 April 2019:
**1. Updated the logic of Annual Statement reminders**
- The “Send to Billing contact” tick box will no longer be selected be default when sending Annual Statements.
- The reminders recipient details will update when the Billing contact information is updated
- Annual Statement reminders will be sent to the Annual Statement recipient if the Billing Contact does not exist in the company profile.

**2. Updated the validation rules for Signing and Billing contact details**
- The Preferred name and Postal address details for Signing and Billing contacts are optional in Corporate Messenger, Trust Register and SuperComply.

**3.ABN/TFN application available for more trust types**
Added a link to complete ABN/TFN application on Collaboration page for the following trust.
- Fixed Trust
- Hybrid trust
- SUIT trust
- NSW Land Tax Unit trust
- Regulation 13.22C trust

**4. ASIC lodgement Status**
- Update logic to display the correct ASIC Status on the lodgement page.

**5. Search function in Trust Register**
- The search function in Trust Register now includes the look up of Appointor and Settlor names
